PredicateInvocationRolePlayerExpression
public class PredicateInvocationRolePlayerExpression
extends ExpressionImpl

Special implementation of ExpressionImpl representing a role-player-constraint of predicate-invocation.

The grammar production rule of the expression is:

predicate-invocation-role-player ::= anchor : value-expression | ...

Author:
Sven Krosse
